OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FA police watchdog has said there needs
OL,7,Fto be a "radical overhaul" of the
OL,8,Fsystem which identifies officers who
OL,9,Fundermine trust and confidence in the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FThe Independent Scrutiny of Police
OL,13,FPowers Panel (ISOPP) said change was
OL,14,Fneeded for the public and the majority
OL,15,Fof the police who do "excellent work."
OL,17,FIt comes after Avon and Somerset
OL,18,FPolice took part in a TV documentary
OL,19,Fexamining cases against their own
OL,20,Fofficers.
