OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FThe three-part Channel 4 Series 'To
OL,7,FCatch a Copper' provides a behind-the-
OL,8,Fscenes look at how the Professional
OL,9,FStandards Department handles
OL,10,Fmisconduct cases.
OL,12,FAvon and Somerset Police said it has
OL,13,Fmade "significant changes" to the
OL,14,Fvetting system and misconduct
OL,15,Fprocesses since the documentary was
OL,16,Ffilmed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
