CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1709132459
OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,F"The landscape has changed
OL,7,Fsignificantly, and we're more robust
OL,8,Fthan ever at rooting out those who
OL,9,Fbetray the values and standards
OL,10,Fthey're expected to uphold, ensuring
OL,11,Fthey cannot serve again," they said.
OL,13,FA force spokesperson added: "We're
OL,14,Fcommitted to changing our culture, so
OL,15,Fthese damaging attitudes and
OL,16,Fbehaviours have no place to thrive and
OL,17,Fare called out for what they are."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
