OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FThe ISOPP is an independent scrutiny
OL,7,Fpanel, which was set up by Avon and
OL,8,FSomerset Police to highlight good
OL,9,Fpractices and identify areas for
OL,10,Fimprovement.
OL,12,FIt is made up of volunteers from
OL,13,Fdiverse backgrounds who want to help
OL,14,Fthe Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,15,Fmonitor the use of force by the
OL,16,Fpolice, such as the use of a taser.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
