PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1709132459
OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FThe group has examined more than one
OL,7,Fthousand cases so far, and said that
OL,8,Fas well as examples of "exceptional
OL,9,Fpolicing," they have seen "poor and
OL,10,Fdamaging" practices.
OL,12,FWhile the independent panel
OL,13,Facknowledged it was a "courageous"
OL,14,Fdecision to open up the force for
OL,15,Fscrutiny, they said they were "shocked
OL,16,Fand disappointed" by the coverage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
