OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F433A1709132459
OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FIt added: "As an independent panel, we
OL,7,Fescalate our questions and challenge
OL,8,FAvon and Somerset Police and the
OL,9,FPolice and Crime Commissioner as to
OL,10,Fwhat they plan to do in the light of
OL,11,Fthe continued police misconduct that
OL,12,Fhas brought policing into disrepute,
OL,13,Fdamaged trust and confidence,
OL,14,Fparticularly in black communities and
OL,15,Fdeters good people from joining the
OL,16,Fpolice."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
