OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said the
OL,7,Fcases shown in the documentary were
OL,8,F"challenging and distressing" and that
OL,9,Fofficers have been receiving
OL,10,Fadditional training.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News, the force's
OL,13,FChief Constable Sarah Crew and added
OL,14,Fthat she "wished they never happened."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
