OL,3,CWatchdog calls for 'radical overhaul'
OL,4,Cof policing following TV documentary
OL,6,FIn a statement, the force added:
OL,7,F"While they are the exception and not
OL,8,Fthe rule, we must not be afraid to
OL,9,Fface into the issues this series
OL,10,Fraises, so we can create stronger ties
OL,11,Fwith all our communities, especially
OL,12,Fthose who have lower levels of
OL,13,Fconfidence in us.
OL,15,F"This is at the very heart of policing
OL,16,Fby consent.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
