OL,6,F"In order to rebuild the public's
OL,7,Ftrust and confidence in policing, we
OL,8,Fmust continue to be open and
OL,9,Ftransparent about the issues and
OL,10,Fchallenges we face, as well as the
OL,11,Factions we're taking to tackle them
OL,12,Fhead-on."
